{"tid":1738501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滕錦光短暫進入理大校園　促留守者今日內全部離開","createTime":"2019-11-19T09:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T09:22:01.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4de57bbd38ffb411f70d43073b66600e7d6a71","tid":1738501,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:16:30.000Z","msg":"理工大學校長滕錦光下午視察理大，於校園A座逗留不足5分鐘後離開。滕錦光表示，校方與警方保持緊密溝通，以保證所有於校園範圍內的人士均能安全離開。<br />\n<br />\n滕錦光說，當校園內的人士不使用武力，警方亦會停止武力，現階段可見相關做法取得成功，呼籲所有仍留守理大校園的人士，今日內和平地離開。<br />\n<br />\n至於有否設下示威者離開校園的死線，滕錦光形容有如隧道盡頭的曙光，只要校園內全部人離開，事情就會解決。被問到為何起初只於校園外圍的位置張望，他說相信大家都關注安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493248-20191119.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493248-20191119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=U%2B24RsvDmKluq6DDuV4MqvtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=9e2fd51f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493248-20191119.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0d216d74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493248-20191119.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6a8d8742d3879fbae1d8e99bcdbe0de16e5cbdc9","tid":1738501,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"成你老母功<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">殺人校長 世代為奴為娼啦</span>"},{"pid":"a135c5ca7022069d89b616ff1fea1f5596b3c0aa","tid":1738501,"uid":259993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"好懷疑理大之後一年上唔上到堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}